            <p>Global warming is primarily caused by human activities that release greenhouse gases into the atmosphere, trapping heat and causing the Earth's temperature to rise. The main culprits are:</p>
            <div class="info-grid">
                <div class="info-card">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611273426858-450d8e3c9fce?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Greenhouse Gases">
